##################################################################################################################

USAGE:: perl post_gatkms_filter.pl 

post_gatkms_filter.pl 
 usage: 
--infile 	 multisample VCF file 
--outfile 	 post filtered VCF file 
--value 	 minimum read depth supporting the variant in atleast one sample (default : 5) 
--help 		 show help 



Limitations: Currently only runnnig for bi-allelic sites; For sites other than bi-allelic is under development


